# AXIOM validator seed list — the canonical, hand-edited default.
#
# One CSV line per validator:  "name", "ed25519 pubkey (64 hex)", "carriers"
#   name     — human label.
#   pubkey   — the validator's Ed25519 identity key. The SDK seals the
#              outbound UMP to it (Ed25519 -> X25519). Empty -> Plain.
#   carriers — comma-separated <SCHEME>:<addr>, how to reach the validator.
#              schemes: email, TOT, FATMAMA, P2P (scheme is case-insensitive).
#
# This file is the single source — validators, Nabla, and every client read
# it. No generator produces it: edit it directly. '#' lines are comments.
